sequenceDiagram
    actor User as Deloitte Employee
    participant UI as Next.js Frontend
    participant API as FastAPI Backend
    participant Val as Input Validator
    participant Embed as Embedding Service<br/>(Qwen3-Embedding-0.6B)
    participant DB as PostgreSQL<br/>(pgvector + ParadeDB)
    participant RR as Cohere Rerank v3.5

    User->>UI: Enter search query
    UI->>API: POST /api/search {query, filters}
    API->>Val: validate(query)

    alt Validation Fails
        Val-->>API: ValidationError (reason)
        API-->>UI: 400 Error + guidance message
        UI-->>User: Display error + suggestions
    else Validation Passes
        Val-->>API: OK
        API->>Embed: generate_embedding(query)
        Embed-->>API: query_vector [1024 dims]

        par Parallel Hybrid Retrieval
            API->>DB: semantic_search(query_vector, top_k=50)
            DB-->>API: semantic_results[]
        and
            API->>DB: bm25_search(query_text, top_k=50)
            DB-->>API: keyword_results[]
        and
            API->>DB: title_similarity(query_vector, top_k=50)
            DB-->>API: title_results[]
        end

        Note over API: rrf_merge(semantic, keyword, title,<br/>title_boost=1.5x) → merged[top 50]
        API->>RR: rerank(query, merged_results, top_n=10)
        RR-->>API: reranked_results[top 10]
        Note over API: filter by RBAC access level
        Note over API: filter by version (show latest only)
        API->>DB: batch fetch document metadata
        DB-->>API: document records[]
        API-->>UI: 200 OK + results[]
        UI-->>User: Display results (title, snippet, author, date, type)
    end
